PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1996-1884 of December 5, 1996, as amended by P.C. 1997-416 and P.C. 1997-1337, which extends the re-appointment of CHARLES A. GRACEY as a temporary member of the Canadian International Trade Tribunal until May 29, 1998.
